user:
Analyze the following dealership insights and generate a comprehensive business impact assessment.

Please provide a structured JSON output with the following sections:
{
  "revenue_impact": {
    "total_projected": "Specific dollar amount",
    "confidence": "high/medium/low",
    "details": [
      "Specific revenue stream with projected increase",
      "Another revenue opportunity with timeframe"
    ]
  },
  "cost_savings": {
    "total_projected": "Specific dollar amount",
    "confidence": "high/medium/low",
    "details": [
      "Specific cost center with savings estimate",
      "Another efficiency opportunity with implementation timeframe"
    ]
  },
  "customer_impact": {
    "score": "1-10 rating",
    "level": "high/medium/low",
    "affected_areas": [
      "Specific customer experience touchpoint",
      "Another area of customer impact"
    ]
  },
  "urgency_factors": [
    "Specific competitive threat or market condition",
    "Time constraint or window of opportunity"
  ],
  "implementation": {
    "timeframe": "Estimated implementation period",
    "complexity": "high/medium/low",
    "resources_needed": [
      "Specific resource or skillset required",
      "Another implementation requirement"
    ]
  },
  "overall_impact": {
    "score": "1-10 rating",
    "justification": "Clear business rationale for the score",
    "risk_flag": true/false
  }
}

Be specific with financial projections and provide clear justification for your impact assessments. Always analyze the impact across multiple dimensions including financial outcome, customer experience, operational efficiency, and competitive advantage.
